          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πί̄νω</span></b> , inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πῑνέμεναι</span>, ipf. iter. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πί̄νεσκε</span>, fut. part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">πῑόμενος</span>, aor. 2 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔπιον</span>,
